  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.3.2">
<l>ottār mikkārai yivaiyāya māmāya</l>
<l>vottā yepporuṭku muyirāyeṉ ṉaippeṟṟa</l>
<l>tāyāyt tantaiyā yaṟiyātaṉa vaṟivitta</l>
<l>vattānī ceytaṉa vaṭiyē ṉaṟiyēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In great illusive power that are these you are equal</l>
<l>to great people who are equal. Being the life of every thing, being the mother</l>
<l>who begot me, being the father, o father who made [me] know the things</l>
<l>[I] don’t know, I, [your] devotee don’t know the things you did.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
